{"tid":2261993,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)我隻貓唔認得佢個姊妹可以點搞?","createTime":"2020-10-28T17:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T04:23:28.000Z","uid":218082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"71a9da1291d9f002cb27e64441ab596986256982","tid":2261993,"uid":218082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"我屋企本身養咗兩隻貓,係孖生姊<br />\n事源早兩日我帶咗隻家姐去睇獸醫,睇完返嚟個細妹因爲陣味唔同咗而唔認得佢<br />\n佢當晚對住家姐勁嬲狂哈氣仲差啲打佢,老豆想制止佢差啲攻擊埋老豆<br />\n平時佢好溫順唔會攻擊人,佢個晚係直頭失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家過咗兩日佢冇之前咁惡,但都會keep住對家姐哈氣又想走去打佢<br />\n因為佢地由細到大都未分開過,一分開一陣間就出事<br />\n咁嘅情況應該點搞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa37057d7e92f126ae0bc93e4bfbc8384aa30416","tid":2261993,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T17:57:37.000Z","msg":"我幫你收留佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e31b73d537ec6f71ba403ad87679eee7e289ae","tid":2261993,"uid":78418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"我之前都試過<br />\n我就由佢哋自己行嚟行去<br />\n如果佢哋wee大家就即刻分開佢哋<br />\n因為去咗獸醫到陣味唔同咗<br />\n過幾日就冇事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fac98257dc0bebb64951f5ea12dfd102dd5ae4b","tid":2261993,"uid":218082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa37057d7e92f126ae0bc93e4bfbc8384aa30416","tid":2261993,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T17:57:37.000Z","msg":"我幫你收留佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply